<p>The 73-year-old wore a black zipper jacket and khaki shorts paired with brown slip-on shoes.</p>

<p>He sported a neatly trimmed gray beard and added a pair of sunglasses.</p>

<p>Arnold, who is often joined by friends and family for his bike trips, was solo on this occasion.</p>

<p>Staying fit: The Hollywood star and former governor of California donned an 'OG' black baseball cap for his exercise session</p>

<p>Proud papa: On Monday evening, Arnold had marked his youngest son Christopher's 23rd birthday with a sweet Instagram post that included a montage of photos</p>

<p> A few hours earlier, Arnold had marked his youngest son Christopher's 23rd birthday with a sweet Instagram post.</p>

<p>The Terminator star shared a collage of images of Christopher and in the accompanying caption, he wrote: 'Happy birthday Christopher! You are such a fantastic son - kind, smart, giving, and everything I could ask for.'</p>

<p>He added: 'I can’t wait to see what you do with this year, but I know I’ll be proud watching! I love you!'</p>

<p>Meanwhile, his son Patrick, 27, posted a photo taken at his brother's birthday celebration with mom Maria Shriver, sister Christina, 29, and their famous father.</p>

<p>Not pictured in the family group was eldest child Katherine, 30, who recently gave birth to her first child with husband Chris Pratt. </p>

<p>Arnold and Maria split in 2011 after 25 years of marriage when it was revealed the actor had fathered a son Joseph Baena with the family's former housekeeper. The exes finalized their divorce in 2017. </p>

<p>Another year: Christopher celebrated his birthday at home on Monday with a birthday cake and candles along with mom Maria Shriver and siblings Patrick and Christina</p>
